# OpenClaw Environment Configuration вЂ” the node's functional parameters (docs/NODE_SPEC.md В§3)
# install.sh copies this to ~/.openclaw/openclaw.env and appends generated values.

# в”Ђв”Ђ Bus в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# NATS server URL вЂ” every subsystem talks through this (loopback by design)
OPENCLAW_NATS=nats://127.0.0.1:4222

# NATS auth token вЂ” REQUIRED server-side (D2 trust floor).
# install.sh generates one (openssl rand -hex 32) and appends it here + embeds
# it in the rendered NATS confs. Do not leave empty on a running node.
# OPENCLAW_NATS_TOKEN=

# в”Ђв”Ђ Node identity в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Role вЂ” 'lead' or 'worker' (default: macOS=lead, Linux=worker)
# OPENCLAW_NODE_ROLE=worker
# Node ID вЂ” auto-detected from hostname if not set
# OPENCLAW_NODE_ID=my-node-name

# в”Ђв”Ђ LLM backend в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Grappe-worker provider = the node's OpenClaw frontend (advanced LLM). D11: a
# grappe/cluster worker MUST be an advanced LLM (claude/openai/gemini/deepseek/
# kimi/minimax/aider), NEVER a local model вЂ” mesh-agent refuses ollama here.
MESH_LLM_PROVIDER=claude
# Local model tag for the EXTRACTION/embedding/probe organ ONLY (never a grappe
# worker's mind). install.sh upgrades this to your RAM tier via check-llm-baseline
# (16GBв†’qwen3:8b В· 32GBв†’qwen3:14b В· 48GBв†’qwen3:32b)
LLM_MODEL=qwen3:8b
# Ollama endpoint (extraction + probes)
LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
# Memory extraction mode вЂ” true = LLM extraction (falls back to regex if the
# model is unreachable; node-watch reports the degradation)
USE_LLM_EXTRACTION=true

# в”Ђв”Ђ Misc в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
OPENCLAW_TIMEZONE=America/Montreal

# в”Ђв”Ђ Optional feature keys (core node needs NONE of these) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=            # cloud extraction/agents via API
# OPENAI_API_KEY=               # openai-provider agents
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=               # Mission Control TTS voice
# DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN=            # mesh-tool-discord (enable its unit after setting)
# OBSIDIAN_API_KEY=             # Obsidian Local REST sync
# KNOWLEDGE_MODEL=Xenova/bge-m3 # embedder override (default shown)
# LLM_TIMEOUT=600000            # extraction generation budget (ms)
